{"tid":2121392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生涉藏棍「撤控舞刀內地男案情更嚴重」  官促控方公平：佢更值得放","createTime":"2020-07-23T09:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T10:30:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e422360d819d35abe902bafd9b7957d0b069313","tid":2121392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/RBM5S3S2EOXW7WHFUH7DBYOT3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FRBM5S3S2EOXW7WHFUH7DBYOT3A%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=fa1af82d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FRBM5S3S2EOXW7WHFUH7DBYOT3A%2F&h=5e58dd6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/RBM5S3S2EOXW7WHFUH7DBYOT3A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學生涉藏棍「撤控舞刀內地男案情更嚴重」 <br />\n官促控方公平：佢更值得放<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】律政司早前撤銷起訴向示威同學持刀揮舞的中大內地生，改以簽保守行為了事，惹公眾譁然。......................................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Tw9SNBXKby4_bIAiIBhM7rZlh28=/1426x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/42SPYANX2UZ33FBFJ26W2IXSB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTw9SNBXKby4_bIAiIBhM7rZlh28%3D%2F1426x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F42SPYANX2UZ33FBFJ26W2IXSB4.jpg&h=5d049d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判官溫紹明曾處理中大內地生揮刀案（圖），直言本案被告更值得撤控。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n被告為17歲中五學生，.................................<br />\n<br />\n溫官重提早前處理內地生在中大校園揮刀一案，律政司堅持批准被告簽保守行為，他指「比較過嚴重性，其實遠超過呢單」。溫官指控方指控本案被告手持伸縮棍，以在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪起訴：「我知控方有酌情權。我處理過好多伸縮棍案件，都係罰一千幾百。我明白控方有權點樣檢控，但應該用得公平。」<br />\n<br />\n溫官又說：「呢個係17歲中五學生，中大揮刀嗰個係大學生，我覺得佢成熟啲添。我當時對單案表達咗意見，律政司都認為可以放佢一馬，fine。咁我就覺得呢單案更多原因值得放。」溫官表明：「法庭唔係話單單都要bind over（簽保守行為），今次被告clear record（無案底），睇唔到有咩原因唔值得過嗰單囉。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pd2EZ-qTGeLqdSAUoz96zH3JoO8=/590x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/II34APM2PQXHWU4QOFMMEAWDPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPd2EZ-qTGeLqdSAUoz96zH3JoO8%3D%2F590x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FII34APM2PQXHWU4QOFMMEAWDPU.jpg&h=dcd2e316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判官溫紹明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「冇嘢阻到法庭表達意見」<br />\n<br />\n他說法庭並非就檢控事宜跟控方商討及討論，但明言：「冇嘢阻到法庭表達意見。既然辯方想同控方商討，咁麻煩控方向律政司表達法庭意見。」主控欲回應卻遭溫官拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n溫官指疫情下法庭積壓大量案件，指「如果有啲案件唔使用審訊方式處理，就可以更善用其他資源。」案件押後至9月4日再繼續審訊。<br />\n<br />\n中大內地生李丹石（21歲）去年11月在大學圖書館外持刀揮舞，並高唱中國國歌，原被控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，上周獲准以兩千元簽保、守行為兩年。"},{"pid":"2da3a415ef716fd909e2486927430b1860327ab6","tid":2121392,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d9c9373d2baed6e039a896320f17e67772041","tid":2121392,"uid":276273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"香港仲有幾多咁有腰骨同良知既官？濁水中一點清泉"},{"pid":"cc475054c87ef6e8441f2978ea5939a307c8bd80","tid":2121392,"uid":111464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"正常嘅法官而家真係買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d22fd306f6298fbffa82aa42c202b5707b840a6","tid":2121392,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cc475054c87ef6e8441f2978ea5939a307c8bd80","tid":2121392,"uid":111464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"正常嘅法官而家真係買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"而家都反撚曬肚<br />\n埋邊嘅就自然pro-Beijing 架啦"},{"pid":"06b2f88ebb5f851ff22a246091721ae955103851","tid":2121392,"uid":206617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"我都唔求有黃官<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只求多啲好似溫官咁，相對持平公正少少既法官<br />\n係呢個法治變左笑話既香港法律界到起碼叫些少清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0306d58ebd2d9de604371102842133b748da4e","tid":2121392,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"真正公正嘅法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ad63241726858582fec94916b3a359d1a892ca","tid":2121392,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"難得一見正常法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c8b786c8cdcff8547d5a118f4fa7c61a5ad459","tid":2121392,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:29:36.000Z","msg":"清泉"},{"pid":"9afb9816ebc828cde00cc748633a3691b6215276","tid":2121392,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}